Chroot repo.  For documenting chroot environments for dhcp, dns, and apache.


Filelist
========
INSTALL-dhcp
  Installing dhcp3-server in order to extract binaries for chroot build.

Makefile
  GNU Makefile to build chroot LaTeX documentation.

VERSION
  chroot LaTeX VERSION file.

TODO
  TODO items for chroot document.

build.xml
  Ant build file to generate PDF from chroot.tex LaTeX file.

chroot.pdf
  Chroot Configuration
  by marcilr@gmail.com   
  Version 1.0       
  This document contains chroot configuration notes for dhcp, bind,
  and apache. Used for configuration of services on home network.

chroot.tex.in 
  Chroot input file to configure with VERSION to generate chroot.tex

dist-build.xml
  Ant build file to build document distribution package. 

fdl.txt
  GNU Free Documentation License
  Version 1.3, 3 November 2008

figsize.sty
  Package to dynamically size figures relative to the page size.




